## Objective target refresh (HardLight)

# Sent to a traitor when their kill/maroon target left the round and a new one was assigned.
objective-target-refresh-rerolled = [color=crimson]Syndicate update:[/color] Your target has left the station. A new target has been assigned: {$name}.

# Sent to a traitor when their kill/maroon target left the round and no replacement could be found.
objective-target-refresh-removed = [color=crimson]Syndicate update:[/color] Your target has left the station and no suitable replacement was found. The objective has been cancelled.
